'This little program shows the speed between passing parameters to Pbob's  
'in a loop and the new command that needs no loop. 
'
Screen Open 0,320,200,4,L
Curs Off : Flash Off 
Cls 0
Box 0,0 To 15,15
Get Bob 1,0,0 To 16,16
Dim X(30),Y(30),Z(30)
For I=1 To 30
   X(I)=Rnd(300)
   Y(I)=Rnd(150)
   Z(I)=1
Next 
Pbob Dbuf False
Reserve Pbobs 30
For I=1 To 30
   Pbob Height I,16
Next 
T=Timer
For I=1 To 500
   For L=1 To 30
      Pbob L,X(L),Y(L),1
   Next 
Next 
Print Timer-T
T=Timer
For I=1 To 500
   Pbob Varptr(X(1)),Varptr(Y(1)),Varptr(Z(1)),1 To 30
Next 
Print Timer-T
Pbob Update 
Wait Key 
End 
